  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      10 patients will be treated alternating daily between prone and supine position for breast
      radiotherapy to compare set-up accuracy. Prone treatment will be given on the odds days and
      supine treatment on the even days.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
